        {
            "content_html": "<img src=\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/43580235?u=a7abf92f16a0e563130967aef2beb65cbf9cf882&v=4\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" alt=\"\"/><br/><p dir=\"auto\">This pull request removes instances of <code class=\"notranslate\">{{EmbedLiveSample}}</code> macro where a <strike>third</strike> fourth parameter is provided.</p>\n<ul dir=\"auto\">\n<li>Most of these are empty: <code class=\"notranslate\">{{EmbedLiveSample('title', 'width', 'height', '')}}</code></li>\n<li>Ones with screenshots are presumably fallbacks when browsers did not support the features demonstrated. Deleting the screenshots in this case as the live sample renders well by itself so a screenshot is redundant.</li>\n</ul>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><strong>Other changes:</strong></p>\n<ul dir=\"auto\">\n<li>Fixing duplicate section headings, using bold text instead for some sections.</li>\n</ul>",
