            "content_html": "<img src=\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/97945148?u=a6895a737c183867bcc85b3dcb06c625158d1701&v=4\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" alt=\"\"/><br/><h3 dir=\"auto\">Description</h3>\n<p dir=\"auto\">This PR adds the CSS data types<code class=\"notranslate\">&lt;color-interpolation-method&gt;</code> and <code class=\"notranslate\">&lt;hue-interpolation-method&gt;</code>, and removes duplicate <code class=\"notranslate\">&lt;hue&gt;</code> descriptions on CSS color functions.</p>\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">Motivation</h3>\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">Additional details</h3>\n<p dir=\"auto\">W3C issue related to hue interpolation: <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"1708665899\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/w3c/csswg-drafts/issues/8838\" data-hovercard-type=\"issue\" data-hovercard-url=\"/w3c/csswg-drafts/issues/8838/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/w3c/csswg-drafts/issues/8838\">w3c/csswg-drafts#8838</a>.</p>\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">Related issues and pull requests</h3>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><span class=\"issue-keyword tooltipped tooltipped-se\" aria-label=\"This pull request closes issue #26435.\">Fixes</span> <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"1684930013\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/mdn/content/issues/26435\" data-hovercard-type=\"issue\" data-hovercard-url=\"/mdn/content/issues/26435/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/mdn/content/issues/26435\">#26435</a>.</p>",
